item.title: How do i port forward with sky BB
item.dc:creator: @qazws qazws
item.description:
@qazws wrote:

ok ill help you[br][size=1]Posted on: July 05, 2007, 10:13:42 AM[/size][hr]go to http://portforward.com/
click portforward on top on left side
scroll down and find your router(easier way is to copy ur dg834gt and hit ctrl-f)
then click the program 1st SMTP Server
then follow the instructions it provides

hope this helps
